BC Simple Flash Player README

What is the BC Simple Flash Player extension?
================================

BC Simple Flash Player is a true eZ Publish extension
that provides an example extension based design with
the required flash, javscript and template override
to provide a flash content object media player.


BC Simple Flash Player version
=======================

The current version of BC Simple Flash Player is 0.4.0
Last Major update: March 25, 2012

You can find details about changes for this
version in doc/changelogs/CHANGELOG-0.4.0


